  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Range was built as a tool to help you limit distractions and make work (or play!) sessions more productive. Embark on a drive by selecting a duration for your session and any tasks or goals you want to complete. Select the environment you’d like to drive through, and customize your vehicle to your liking! Set off on your relaxing drive, complete tasks as you go, and decompress with a break before your next session.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3584150/extras/ab26b787ced23a87c137371be7003562.avif?t=1748514215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3584150/extras_big/ab26b787ced23a87c137371be7003562.avif?t=1748514215 width=800 height=224 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you complete sessions (and breaks!), level up with rewarded experience and build up Credits. Credits can be spent to unlock the full roster of 8 customizable vehicles and 10 different vehicle accessories. As you level up, you automatically unlock 4 different playable environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3584150/extras/02aeea441f82d896c52b88eac30ca0d4.avif?t=1748514215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3584150/extras_big/02aeea441f82d896c52b88eac30ca0d4.avif?t=1748514215 width=800 height=224 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you play and level up, enjoy drives through new areas - the Snowy Mountains, Coastal Highway, Canyon Straights, and Redwood Forest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3584150/extras/3b07676957fb712183cef1927f5ada6c.avif?t=1748514215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3584150/extras_big/3b07676957fb712183cef1927f5ada6c.avif?t=1748514215 width=800 height=224 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you complete sessions and tasks, visit the Log to keep track of everything you’ve accomplished.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Range was built as a tool to help you limit distractions and make work (or play!) sessions more productive. Embark on a drive by selecting a duration for your session and any tasks or goals you want to complete. Select the environment you’d like to drive through, and customize your vehicle to your liking! Set off on your relaxing drive, complete tasks as you go, and decompress with a break before your next session.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3584150/extras/ab26b787ced23a87c137371be7003562.avif?t=1748514215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3584150/extras_big/ab26b787ced23a87c137371be7003562.avif?t=1748514215 width=800 height=224 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you complete sessions (and breaks!), level up with rewarded experience and build up Credits. Credits can be spent to unlock the full roster of 8 customizable vehicles and 10 different vehicle accessories. As you level up, you automatically unlock 4 different playable environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3584150/extras/02aeea441f82d896c52b88eac30ca0d4.avif?t=1748514215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3584150/extras_big/02aeea441f82d896c52b88eac30ca0d4.avif?t=1748514215 width=800 height=224 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you play and level up, enjoy drives through new areas - the Snowy Mountains, Coastal Highway, Canyon Straights, and Redwood Forest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3584150/extras/3b07676957fb712183cef1927f5ada6c.avif?t=1748514215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3584150/extras_big/3b07676957fb712183cef1927f5ada6c.avif?t=1748514215 width=800 height=224 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you complete sessions and tasks, visit the Log to keep track of everything you’ve accomplished.</p>",
